I'm exhausted, I'm tired and need your help.

https://www.gofundme.com/f/marcusdibblelegalfees

Hey Dibble,


Not sure if you remember me, but last time you were in Albany and going to Anytime Fitness (3 years ago) i rocked up at like 3am and you were there and it was only us haha. When life puts you in tough situations dont say why me, say try me.


luv ya man
